{"tid":2215722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［法律撚入］樓上成日倒水落嚟","createTime":"2020-09-24T07:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T13:13:14.000Z","uid":178220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5706c1241a8eb159e8f33b848a839969122ab405","tid":2215722,"uid":178220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"如題，樓上成日倒水落嚟，<br />\n都持續咗年幾兩年（或者更多年），<br />\n日日都係咁，早午晚幾次。<br />\n<br />\n屋企人一直無為意，但呢排我喺屋企多咗，<br />\n呢幾日終於忍唔住，的起心肝想投訴佢，<br />\n今日佢一倒水我就拍片，<br />\n真係影到樓上拆開冷氣機個喉刻意倒水落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲水仲要微黃色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拍咗片有哂證據，諗住一陣晏啲落樓下管理處投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱八卦上Google搵「樓上倒水 香港法律」，<br />\n發現原來呢類case喺香港地都幾常見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲case仲更加嚴重添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就想開post諮詢各方意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者大家分享下類似經歷、如何處理等等，<br />\n討論討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講翻，睇咗幾個其他論壇嘅討論帖，<br />\n發現大部分人都叫樓主去樓下管理處投訴，<br />\n但其實去樓下投訴係80%解決唔到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就好奇問下「樓上倒水」係咪犯法嘅呢？<br />\n或者刻意倒水出街又犯咗邊條法例？<br />\n感謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry第一次開post希望無1999"},{"pid":"2dd8e06a4029c0b7bff0363d3f81961f6c7a7b09","tid":2215722,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T07:46:02.000Z","msg":"高空擲物冇分液體定固體"},{"pid":"c101c6cb48c1fb966c769356f5cea161764dbd8b","tid":2215722,"uid":178220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dd8e06a4029c0b7bff0363d3f81961f6c7a7b09","tid":2215722,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T07:46:02.000Z","msg":"高空擲物冇分液體定固體"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"咁即係告佢高空擲物都可以告到佢甩褲？<br />\n雖然本身唔係想告到佢甩褲，<br />\n但都想知道有無其他關於倒污水出街<br />\n更加specific嘅條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw唔該哂"}]}